                                    h5(class='highlight') The Artist
                                    h3(class='claim') Rudolf Heltzel is unique &mdash; a master of design and technical expertise in jewellery making, with extraordinary artistic talent.
                                    p(class='paragraph') Rudolf Heltzel is renowned as one of the finest haute couture jewellery designers worldwide. Over the past six decades, the originality and quality of Rudolf's work has set him apart. Each of his pieces has a timeless aesthetic, is crafted meticulously by hand using some of the world’s oldest jewellery techniques, and has inimitable balance. His thoughtful designs and impeccable workmanship have won him international acclaim.
